        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2"> Personally, I used all my class guild points to train in research everytime I dinged, until lvl 49. I didn't find anything else that would help me. That way I ended up with 151 in research. I was able to research the spells I needed and I can also help other casters that need it.</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
