        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2"> I also worried I wouldn't get the spells researched the level I would need them, but I find the real spells to worry about are the drop only spells. Talk about a pain in the ass, I still don't have the 39th level Chilling Embrace.</P><P>The only spells I really had trouble with was the 49th level research, which took about 8 hours worth of searching for to get all the words.</P><P>I went the research route, but I would recommend that you find a friendly high level to slap them together for you. Don't forget to offer to donate for the service, it'll save you tons of plat in the long run.</P><P>- Ryptor, Heretic of Tunare</P><P>** Quidquid latine dictum sit, altum sonatur **<BR><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
